            "type": "sound",
            "phoneme": "/z/",
            "showQuotes": false
          },
          " and hold it. Zzzzzzzz."
        ]
      },
      "There it is! Do you feel your throat buzzing? That's your **Buzzer** turning on!",
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "value": [
